Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.89,0:00:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A racing second hand,\Na shooting comet!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.60,0:00:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan's logic is the tonic for\Nhearts tired by modern society!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.94,0:00:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's the Kaitou Kid special!\NDetective and thief square off!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.66,0:00:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single\Ntruth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:14.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid but\Nhas the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.33,0:00:16.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.16,0:01:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm high school student\NKudo Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went with Mori Ran,\Nchildhood friend and classmate,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.29,0:01:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to an amusement park,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.92,0:01:57.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,where I witnessed a suspicious\Ndeal involving a man in black.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:02:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so engrossed with watching\Nthat I didn't see his partner hiding!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.39,0:02:05.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was knocked down\Nand given a poison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up,\Nmy body had shrunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.39,0:02:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they learned\NKudo Shinichi was alive,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.86,0:02:14.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,people around me would be in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.07,0:02:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After following Prof. Agasa's\Nadvice to conceal my identity,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.11,0:02:19.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran asked me my\Nname and I quickly said...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.49,0:02:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,... "Edogawa Conan!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.03,0:02:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, to uncover\Ninformation about them,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.91,0:02:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I moved in with Ran\Nand her detective father.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.04,0:02:36.05,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan vs. Kaitou Kid
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.96,0:02:34.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan vs. Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou #1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He's an older thief that\Nall the young girls are crazy about!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:50.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Older"?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.39,0:02:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your dad's a detective\Nand you never heard of him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean\NI love following crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:03:00.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But hear me out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.20,0:03:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you want my\Ndad to catch this thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.24,0:03:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know Beika Museum's\Nexhibit of world-famous jewels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy submitted our family gem,\Nthe lucky Black Star pearl,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and wants it protected
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:23.97,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from Kaitou #1412's evil grasp!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.43,0:03:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why ask my\Ndad and not the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:33.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do that! The police would\Nhaul him off if they caught him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.31,0:03:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if your dad catches him,\Nhe might let us see his face!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.74,0:03:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His face?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Don't you\Nwonder what he looks like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.70,0:03:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,# 1412 has the entire\Nworld going crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet he's a fabulous guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.45,0:03:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like Harrison Ford or John Lennon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:55.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You live so happily...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.96,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The light's green, Sonoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:03:59.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.80,0:04:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if he\Nwas like Brad Pitt!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.48,0:04:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.44,0:04:22.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! The light's red!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, that was Shinichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was Shinichi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.33,0:04:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure it wasn't just a look-alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.87,0:04:35.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You passed by\NShinichi-{\i1}niichan {\i0}in Shibuya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.17,0:04:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.18,0:04:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he wouldn't respond!\NIsn't that horrible?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.39,0:04:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now! I wasn't in Shibuya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.34,0:04:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And besides, I haven't\Neven changed bodies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.47,0:04:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, he's probably sick of you.\NJust forget about that mystery dweeb.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.56,0:04:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... He was walking with a girl, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was someone else!\NDon't worry about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.24,0:05:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.07,0:05:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, do they really want me to\Ncatch this Kaitou something-or-other?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou #1412!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.54,0:05:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with the 1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.33,0:05:21.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one's really\Nsure where it comes from.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.67,0:05:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,According to Sonoko, he steals art\Nand jewels from all over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:31.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and his top secret FBI or CIA
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.01,0:05:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,or Interpol number was 1412.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.64,0:05:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"International Criminal Number"\Nor Interpol number was 1412.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.19,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The leading theory is that people\Nlearned the number and it just stuck!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:44.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds fake to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:48.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently he has a different\Nname in Japan, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:50.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's probably just word play.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like "The Crazy Thief" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.12,0:06:02.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think it was\Nanything that old man-like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dumb. Who cares about some thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.47,0:06:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.22,0:06:13.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah. I have a\Ncopy of a weird warning letter
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.85,0:06:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that Kaitou #1412\Nsent to Sonoko's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.23,0:06:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A weird warning letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.23,0:06:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't make any sense!\NIt's like a code!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.73,0:06:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"April Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.61,0:06:30.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When the moon splits the two,\NI shall enter upon waves
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.45,0:06:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,in the name of the black star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.95,0:06:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou..."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.62,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's torn here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Sonoko's father tore\Nit up in anger when it arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then taped it back together.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, this makes no sense at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.55,0:06:53.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All I do get is that "April Fools"\Nmeans he'll show up on April 1st...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.47,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! I thought you went to bed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.31,0:06:55.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lemme see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.93,0:06:57.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.86,0:07:13.49,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Museum, 1:42 PM, March 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.49,0:07:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.49,0:07:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like all the police in\NTokyo have been mobilized...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.50,0:07:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he really is\Na big international thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that work and\NI still didn't break the code...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.67,0:07:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:35.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I truly appreciate your\Nlistening to my daughter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're 100-men strong with
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.35,0:07:42.31,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki Shiro (51)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.85,0:07:40.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a detective like you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.06,0:07:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you,\NDetective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:49.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just one measly thief.\NI'll capture him with no trouble at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure you will! You haven't\Neven cracked the code yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:08:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the largest black\Npearl in the world, the Black Star?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. The Suzuki family has\Nbeen blessed with prosperity
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.25,0:08:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,ever since my\Ngrandfather first purchased it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.79,0:08:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the family's guardian angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.38,0:08:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Security sure is tight\Nfor the day before the theft.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.14,0:08:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. All we got from\Nthe letter was the date.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.85,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm told that security will be\Non full detail starting tonight--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.69,0:08:29.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's no telling from when\Nor where Kaitou #1412 will strike.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told you! The river!\NDeploy men along the river bank!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.37,0:08:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou #1412 plans to sneak inside
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:42.83,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaki Shintaro (49)
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,from the nearby Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.83,0:08:46.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You cracked the code?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.75,0:08:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure did!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "enter upon waves"\Nbit refers to the Teimuzu River!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.17,0:08:58.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Teimuzu River is the only\Nplace in the vicinity with waves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you Mori from Section 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sloppy, Commissioner!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.40,0:09:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.31,0:09:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you get it? "Waves" means the ocean,\Nwhich means "{\i1}oki{\i0}" (coast).
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.65,0:09:15.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And "star" means a pop star!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.28,0:09:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, the idol star\Nwho performs live tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the nearby Beika Town Hall,\NOkino Yoko-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.87,0:09:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's more, her last\Nsong will be "Moon Lady"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.04,0:09:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"When the moon splits\Nthe two" means that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kaitou #1412 will come from\Nthe vicinity of Beika Town Hall
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.18,0:09:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the show ends at 9:00 pm!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.56,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you say...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.52,0:09:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that does make sense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.35,0:09:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well done, Detective Mori!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.85,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Have Teams C through E\Nassemble near Beika Town Hall!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.65,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.44,0:09:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.61,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I haven't broken\Nthe code either...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, where's the fellow who\Nwas transferred to us last month?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.75,0:10:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The inspector? He took some\Nofficers somewhere this morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.46,0:10:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.46,0:10:17.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's 2:00!\NWhy don't we have lunch nearby?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys gonna have lunch?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.51,0:10:21.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ate on the way here...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.47,0:10:22.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.35,0:10:25.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a minute! Could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.22,0:10:27.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:36.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Checking the direction\Nwith my watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.78,0:10:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. First, you point the\Nhour hand toward the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.45,0:10:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Japan's in the northern hemisphere,\Nso halfway between it and 12
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.87,0:10:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is where south is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.79,0:10:56.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just testing something\NShinichi-{\i1}niichan {\i0}told me, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.92,0:11:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which means south is at\N1 o'clock, and southeast at 2:30!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.60,0:11:12.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aha! I've figured you out,\NKaitou #1412!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.27,0:11:16.73,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,11:04 PM, March 31st
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fast asleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.17,0:11:36.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agasa here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.13,0:11:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Shinichi! Eh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to find\Nout about Kaitou #1412?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, Professor.\NHe should be in my dad's crime files.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what do you need it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.52,0:11:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to know about\Nhim before I meet him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.98,0:11:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet him?! You know where he is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.94,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup! I've figured out his route inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you tell the police?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.53,0:12:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suddenly wanna see it, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the face of a retro thief who sends\Nwarning notices in this day and age!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.67,0:12:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The "two" in "when\Nthe moon splits the two"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.26,0:12:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,refers to a satellite and the sun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.97,0:12:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the splitting refers to the moon\Ncreating an eclipse between them...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then he'll show up between\N12:30 and 4:00 am when BS TV is off!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.64,0:12:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! The Black Star's initials\Nare BS (Broadcast Satellite)!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:44.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the "waves" refer to\Na satellite signal...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.65,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...then he'll be coming from\Nthe direction of the BS signal!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The BS signal is sent from\Nsouth to west at a 45 degree angle
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:57.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and from 42.3 degrees above the horizon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.08,0:13:03.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The only place that fits the bill\Nis the roof of the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.31,0:13:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! A strange kid ran\Ninto the hotel! What do we do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing. There's only\None person I'm after.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And not even he\Ncould dress up as a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.58,0:13:39.79,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Employees Only
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beika Museum is...\Nright around there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.52,0:14:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,12:28.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.56,0:14:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I just wait for him to show up...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.28,0:14:09.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello? Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.03,0:14:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Shinichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.74,0:14:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I checked your dad's files\Nwith recent newspaper articles.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou #1412 is enveloped\Nin quite a bit of mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.38,0:14:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His first appearance\Nwas in Paris eighteen years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.38,0:14:28.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He suddenly disappeared ten\Nyears later and was presumed dead,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.01,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he's back after eight years\Nand is primarily active in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.60,0:14:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eighteen years ago?\NHe must be pretty old then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has all kinds of names...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.11,0:14:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Modern Lupin,"\N"The Moonlight Magician"...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.36,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's one alias\Nthat people like the most...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.95,0:14:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alias?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.45,0:15:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A young novelist interested\Nin the crafty Kaitou #1412
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.96,0:15:05.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once jokingly read\Nthe number like so...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.04,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"K I D."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"K I D"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.47,0:15:14.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.\NKaitou #1412 is known as...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...the Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.53,0:15:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He landed silently before me,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to disturb\Nthe stillness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:39.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Together with a fearless smile,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.29,0:15:41.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as if he saw through everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.07,0:16:10.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on, Shinichi? Shin--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.99,0:16:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A cape and a silk hat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.12,0:16:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An impenetrable stance...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:27.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't make out his face,\Nbut he's surprisingly young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.42,0:16:32.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His thirties. Twenties?\NNo, even younger!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, little boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.64,0:16:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing up here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fireworks!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.77,0:16:48.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.94,0:16:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A strange flash and sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.65,0:16:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Above the Haido City Hotel,\Nsouthwest of the museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.61,0:16:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I check it out,\NCommissioner?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.33,0:17:00.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course you shall!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.37,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! A helicopter!\NI think it noticed!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.17,0:17:09.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems you're no ordinary kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Edogawa Conan. A detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.22,0:17:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you be escaping,\NKaitou Kid-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.09,0:17:20.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The helicopter will\Nbe here any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.64,0:17:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only have one chance to\Nget him with my tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.85,0:17:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant he\Nturns away to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A radio?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.74,0:17:39.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chaki here! Kaitou Kid sighted\Non top of the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:44.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all patrol\Ncars in Beika and Haido
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all helicopters\Nin the air above Beika!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Proceed to the scene at once\Nand capture the Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.42,0:17:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's using my voice!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.05,0:17:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! That's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.80,0:18:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's his trap!\NAll units, return at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.76,0:18:04.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Helicopter #1!\NI'm above the hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.39,0:18:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sighting confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.35,0:18:07.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.56,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think he sent the orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.61,0:18:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Nakamori!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attention all officers\Ninside the Haido City Hotel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid's on the roof! Rush\Nto the scene at once! Seize him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.33,0:18:24.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's incredible...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.41,0:18:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He can imitate any\Nvoice without a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.29,0:18:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your voice is on the radio!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:34.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's the Kid! He's using my
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.50,0:18:36.34,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakamori Ginzo (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.13,0:18:36.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,voice to bring us to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's insane!\NWhy on earth would he do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:42.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.98,0:18:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Satisfied, Detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.82,0:18:55.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Freeze, Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.48,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my. Inspector Nakamori.\NYou certainly arrived quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.40,0:19:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ha! You knew I cracked your\Ncode and had the place staked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you might hang-glide in,\Nso I checked everyone in the hotel
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.58,0:19:13.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and fortified the main entrance,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.75,0:19:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I never expected you to go\Naround Toto Tower and then land here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.97,0:19:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget about the pearl!\NYou have nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.51,0:19:28.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only here to observe you tonight.\NI don't plan to steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.47,0:19:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.39,0:19:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? I clearly wrote\Nso at the start of the letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.69,0:19:37.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"April Fools." It was a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.19,0:19:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let him escape! Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.16,0:19:44.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A flash grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.12,0:19:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you aware, little boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}kaitou {\i0}is a creative artist\Nwho skillfully steals his prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.37,0:19:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a detective is\Nnothing more than a critic
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who finds fault in\Nwhat is left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.50,0:19:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.34,0:20:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.55,0:20:06.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.68,0:20:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He vanished!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.22,0:20:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Helicopters! Track him using radar!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It only shows our\Nthree helicopters in the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.61,0:20:20.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Has he gotten away again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.69,0:20:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane! No one\Ncan just disappear like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:30.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.20,0:20:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"On March 19th, I will appear\Non the Queen Selizabeth
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.17,0:20:40.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,leaving from Yokohama Port\Nto steal the real Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Kaitou Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.30,0:20:48.85,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,March 19th\N--Queen Selizabeth, Yokohama Port
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.01,0:20:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please cancel it,\NCommissioner Chaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're dealing with the Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.77,0:20:55.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let him get near the jewel\Nwith such lousy security as that!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:57.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be like that,\NNakamori-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.98,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tonight's party is\Nfull of important people!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:03.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't do anything rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.74,0:21:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, we'll lose face if we\Ncancel the party out of fear of him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:14.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry. It'll take three hours\Nfor the ship to get to Tokyo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.71,0:21:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a floating prison! Even if he\Ndoes get on, he's like a rat in a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.30,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year marks Suzuki\NIndustries' 60th anniversary.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is entirely because\Nof the support from you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.97,0:21:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please forget about\Nsneak thieves for tonight
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.73,0:21:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy this elegant and grand\Nparty to which 500 have been invited!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.44,0:21:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have devised a
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.11,0:21:51.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki Tomoko (43)
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.41,0:21:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,special plan for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.37,0:21:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please open the small boxes\Ngiven to you before you boarded.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.12,0:21:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are my letter of challenge\Nto any foolish thieves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.63,0:22:01.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is--
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.63,0:22:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! These are our family's symbol,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.67,0:22:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the Kaitou Kid's\Nprey tonight! The Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.68,0:22:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only one is real, of course.\NAnd only I know to whom it was given.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.85,0:22:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest are imitation pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.65,0:22:22.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then.\NPlease put them on your chests
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.86,0:22:27.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and tell the Kid, "Go ahead\Nand take it, if you dare"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:32.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that's assuming he\Nmanages to determine which one is real
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.70,0:22:35.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,during the three hours we're at sea!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.66,0:22:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your mom's pretty smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Sonoko?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.17,0:22:43.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't find my sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.92,0:22:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me she's still at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:47.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.72,0:22:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! The ship already left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.01,0:22:51.68,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Suzuki Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.47,0:22:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How come?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's my line!\NDo you know what time it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.39,0:23:00.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the commissioner called to\Nsay he was delaying it two hours...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.39,0:23:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Daddy's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.48,0:23:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.28,0:23:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did the company president go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.41,0:23:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He went to the restroom...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.79,0:23:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see! He got on\Nboard disguised as the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.75,0:23:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.76,0:23:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've given me a chance to\Ntear off that bold mask of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.23,0:23:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! Kaitou #1412 disguised\Nhimself as Daddy to get on the ship?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.53,0:23:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just found his disguise\Nand props in the bathroom!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.28,0:23:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The officers are checking it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.16,0:24:03.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is him. I doubt\Nthey'll find any evidence...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.46,0:24:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.58,0:24:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Out looking for you,\Nsince you didn't come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.42,0:24:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was worried\NKaitou #1412 had caught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.80,0:24:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not "#1412."
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.43,0:24:22.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name is Kaitou Kid!\NGet it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.81,0:24:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.81,0:24:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.94,0:24:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector Nakamori. He works\Nfull-time pursuing the Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.32,0:24:40.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you, he's a reliable knight\Nwe hired to protect the Black Star.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.66,0:24:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Still, Madam!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:43.21,0:24:49.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All 500 people here\Nare wearing black pearls!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.88,0:24:55.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And except for the real one,\Nthey're all imitations!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:24:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't guard it unless\NI know which one is real...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.14,0:25:03.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all look alike,\Nbut they're still imitations.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.68,0:25:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Close scrutiny could\Nnarrow it down a bit;
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.31,0:25:11.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,among them are dull\Nand dreary ones such as mine
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.44,0:25:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and excessively\Nshiny rubbish such as yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.49,0:25:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But checking every\Nperson in this crowd would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.12,0:25:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll give you a special hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.04,0:25:30.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Star, the black pearl\Nwith a peacock-green luster
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.67,0:25:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that fascinated my\Ngrandfather sixty years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.76,0:25:38.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is with someone\Nespecially worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.30,0:25:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Worthy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.68,0:25:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidentally, that someone\Nis one out of five hundred...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.85,0:25:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be a woman,\Nif the jewel suits them...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.36,0:25:52.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, but it suits you, too, Mori-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.53,0:25:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so it is you!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,lt's good to see you again!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.82,0:25:59.16,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Hatamoto Joji (41)
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.86,0:25:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for your help a while back!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.87,0:26:02.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you the Hatamoto Group's--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.41,0:26:05.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thanks to this fine\Nwoman and the president,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.87,0:26:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've opened up more restaurants!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.67,0:26:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In fact, tonight's meal is my own--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.17,0:26:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So sorry, Joji-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.96,0:26:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems Mr. Suzuki won't be there,
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.96,0:26:18.18,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Mifune Takuya (26)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.92,0:26:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,thanks to the Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.97,0:26:19.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your flattery food will go to waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.93,0:26:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're as reprehensible as ever!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.22,0:26:23.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing of the sort!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.56,0:26:27.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy from the\NYotsui girl's birthday party...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.06,0:26:30.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You're not wearing yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.69,0:26:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate childish games like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.32,0:26:37.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll seem suspicious\Nif you don't wear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.11,0:26:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.07,0:26:44.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Ayako-{\i1}san{\i0} isn't here?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.99,0:26:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she couldn't make it...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.99,0:26:49.96,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Tomizawa Yuzo (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.50,0:26:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's too bad...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.42,0:26:53.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Suzuki\NIndustries party, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.42,0:26:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's teeming with rich kids\Nand company presidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.42,0:26:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran's taking a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.47,0:27:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably lost somewhere!\NRan has no sense of direction!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.10,0:27:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who has no sense of direction?!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.60,0:27:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Ran! I didn't see you there!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.93,0:27:10.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Police Commissioner Chaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.65,0:27:14.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You may have already heard,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.36,0:27:18.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but that pesky villain has\Nsomehow boarded the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.99,0:27:21.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know,\Nhe's a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.82,0:27:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He possesses an immeasurable\Nevil talent that he uses
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.83,0:27:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to learn about his target\Nand fully imitate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.08,0:27:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even down to their face,\Nvoice, and personality!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.67,0:27:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He may even be among you already!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.05,0:27:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Normally, we would carefully\Ninspect each and every person,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.13,0:27:45.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but we'll refrain\Nfrom such incivility here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.68,0:27:46.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Passwords!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.81,0:27:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pair up with the person next\Nto you and decide on a password!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.44,0:27:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it! That way he\Ncan't keep disguising himself,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.82,0:28:00.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which will allow the\Npolice to single him out!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.15,0:28:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should our password be?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.70,0:28:09.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, when I say "Holmes"...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.24,0:28:10.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I'll say "Lupin"!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.46,0:28:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you doing, Power Room?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.67,0:28:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, this is--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.55,0:28:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.89,0:28:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your passwords are pointless.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.64,0:28:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.89,0:28:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Star is\Nalready in my hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.85,0:28:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:33.98,0:28:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, dear. It's the pesky thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:37.06,0:28:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to punish\Nthis scheming boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.12,0:28:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.46,0:28:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you done?!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.46,0:28:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no need to worry,\NInspector. After all...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.13,0:29:01.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.97,0:29:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My guards caught him\Nin the tablecloth
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.14,0:29:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,after I pretended to shoot\Nhim with this model gun.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.23,0:29:18.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. He's a brilliant magician\NI hired as entertainment...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.56,0:29:21.53,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanada Kazumi (27) - Magician
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.56,0:29:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Sanada Kazumi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.53,0:29:25.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's give him a round of\Napplause for acting out
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.24,0:29:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Kaitou Kid's\Npitiable end for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.62,0:29:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Kaitou Kid is an expert magician--\Nthe perfect role for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.58,0:29:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The two of us do happen to\Nbe artists who deceive the eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.17,0:29:42.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Artists?!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.01,0:29:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I'm a magician by nature.\NA thief is no match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.26,0:29:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, then! Please come to the stage!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.85,0:29:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show you some of my magic!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.52,0:29:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A {\i1}kaitou {\i0}is a creative artist\Nwho skillfully steals his prey,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.94,0:30:00.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but a detective is\Nnothing more than a critic
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.73,0:30:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who finds fault\Nin what is left behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.11,0:30:07.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.16,0:30:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's him! He's somewhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.03,0:30:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll begin with a simple card trick!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.50,0:30:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. I've always\Nbeen the skeptical type.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.92,0:30:22.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,May I cut that deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.63,0:30:26.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Certainly. Would any\Nothers like to as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.51,0:30:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?! Who's the Kaitou Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.97,0:30:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.60,0:30:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They all seem suspicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.02,0:30:36.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's what she said...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.94,0:30:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The black pearl is with\Nsomeone especially worthy of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.69,0:30:44.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I knew what that meant!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.86,0:30:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.53,0:30:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right! Spilled cards\Nwon't ruin my luck ({\i1}tsuki{\i0}).
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.87,0:30:56.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moon ({\i1}tsuki{\i0})?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.00,0:31:02.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, didn't you have a\Nlist of everyone at this party?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.54,0:31:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.34,0:31:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.84,0:31:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This? Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.05,0:31:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.93,0:31:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, ladies!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:13.10,0:31:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me give you a card in return!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:15.97,0:31:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.98,0:31:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! First, let me use my\NX-ray eye to read your minds
Dialogue: 0,0:31:23.11,0:31:25.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and predict your card!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.65,0:31:28.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.99,0:31:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.53,0:31:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.57,0:31:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he said that in the 2nd letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:36.41,0:31:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured it out, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.79,0:31:41.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The location of your prey, that is!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.88,0:31:48.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pigeon ({\i1}hato{\i0})? Hato? Heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.26,0:31:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Ace of Hearts, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.72,0:31:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please pick any card you wish!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.22,0:31:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! The right! The right one!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.56,0:32:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"As Caesar was with Cleopatra,\NI am already by your side.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.36,0:32:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kaitou Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.15,0:32:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.90,0:32:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.94,0:32:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everyone!\NConfirm your passwords!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.11,0:32:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Nakamori-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Don't tell\Nme it's already been stolen!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.37,0:32:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he doesn't have it yet,\Nnor has he escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.37,0:32:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's simply confusing us\Nto make things work his way!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.34,0:32:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry, we can catch him!\NHe's not a wizard!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.80,0:32:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a human being\Nwho relies on tricks!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:45.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaitou Kid really left a message?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:45.06,0:32:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep! It was on\Nthe card Ran just picked!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.48,0:32:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But when and how\Ndid he put this in there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.11,0:32:57.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid is crafty!\NEverything about him is a mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.24,0:33:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All we know is that he's\Nsomewhere in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.79,0:33:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please calm down, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.37,0:33:09.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean he knows\Nwhere the real pearl is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.59,0:33:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he did,\Nthis is a floating prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.43,0:33:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could he possibly\Nmake off with the Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.01,0:33:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,with this police presence?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.49,0:33:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! We'll arrive in\NTokyo Harbor in thirty minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.45,0:33:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Seal all the exits!\NLet no one outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.33,0:33:48.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to show yourself,\NKaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.71,0:33:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is your only chance to\Nstrike while everyone's restless!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.96,0:33:57.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran! Where'd your pearl go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.34,0:33:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.85,0:34:03.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! Could someone\Npick up that pearl?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.69,0:34:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:08.40,0:34:09.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that sound?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.48,0:34:13.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The pearl! It exploded!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.69,0:34:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me the Kid rigged them!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.45,0:34:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget this!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.33,0:34:24.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not wearing this thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.25,0:34:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, everyone! Calm down!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.21,0:34:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.42,0:34:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.59,0:34:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Thank you, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.76,0:34:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.93,0:34:45.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.77,0:34:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Your pearl is gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.82,0:34:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid! He stole the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.45,0:35:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! So you were\Nwearing the real one?!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.82,0:35:06.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! We can't hold them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.83,0:35:13.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inspector! A large\Ngroup has gotten out!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.84,0:35:16.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid's with them! Capture him!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.34,0:35:17.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.46,0:35:19.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}! Let's go catch him, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.67,0:35:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:21.93,0:35:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know who the Kaitou Kid is!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.45,0:35:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A letter declaring the upcoming theft\Nof the Suzuki family's Black Star
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.54,0:35:51.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,arrived at Sonoko's house.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.46,0:35:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sender was one Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.63,0:36:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Upon cracking his code, I waited\Nfor him atop the Haido City Hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.34,0:36:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He landed silently before me
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.47,0:36:06.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so as not to disturb\Nthe stillness of the night.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.14,0:36:09.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only had one chance\Nto use my tranquilizer gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:09.52,0:36:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The instant he turned away to escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.27,0:36:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But instead of running, he imitated\Nmultiple voices without a machine
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.23,0:36:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to lure the police in,\Nand then vanished like smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.90,0:36:25.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that remained was another letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:26.41,0:36:28.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against Inspector Nakamori's protests,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.45,0:36:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Suzuki Industries' 60th anniversary\Nboat party began as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.71,0:36:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sonoko's mother,\NSuzuki Tomoko, devised a plan
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.17,0:36:40.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that looked to spell\Nfailure for the Kaitou Kid,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.26,0:36:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he blew up the pearls and stole\Nthe Black Star during the confusion!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.18,0:36:49.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've figured out who you are, Kaitou Kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.98,0:36:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! You didn't find the Kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.35,0:37:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We checked all the passengers\Nwho left the room earlier, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.40,0:37:07.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has to be on board still!\NCheck every last person on the ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.28,0:37:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.87,0:37:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how did he know she was\Nwearing the real Black Star?!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.83,0:37:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the engine room,\NConan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.09,0:37:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is the Kaitou Kid really in here?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.93,0:37:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}. Do you\Nknow about the language of jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.35,0:37:34.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The language of jewels?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.77,0:37:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pearl means "moon" or "woman."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.06,0:37:42.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of the passengers on board,\Nthe only woman with moons in her name
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.69,0:37:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Suzuki Tomoko-{\i1}san{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.82,0:37:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, she had the real one!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how does that\Ntell you who the Kid is?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.83,0:37:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.12,0:38:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know how the card\Nyou chose had his message?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.00,0:38:02.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.13,0:38:08.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a basic trick in which the magician\Nused the pigeon in his right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.01,0:38:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to distract the audience while\Nhe switched decks in his left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.10,0:38:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the chosen card would be\Nfixed regardless of who cut the deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.94,0:38:22.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So if the message\Nwas on that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.69,0:38:26.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...does that mean\NKaitou Kid was that magician?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.61,0:38:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! I watched the whole time,\Nbut he never got near the lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.24,0:38:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.87,0:38:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one other person\Nwho could've switched cards!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.58,0:38:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That person made them fall,\Npretended to pick them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.96,0:38:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then removed a card\Nand added the message!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.96,0:38:52.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They hid it in their palm and\Npretended to pull it from the deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.22,0:38:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Ran-{\i1}neechan{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I say, Kaitou Kid-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.86,0:39:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper #1!\NHe hasn't fled outside!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.49,0:39:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Chopper #2!\NNo suspicious people on deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.28,0:39:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Surveillance!\NSonar and radar show nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.16,0:39:19.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Keep your eyes peeled!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.00,0:39:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All onboard officers are\Nto split up onto each floor
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.08,0:39:24.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and capture the Kid on sight!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.34,0:39:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't let a familiar face fool you!\NHe's a master of disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.14,0:39:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You switched places with\NRan when she left to find me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.98,0:39:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Impressive. I hadn't noticed at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.90,0:39:50.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After becoming Ran, you agitated\Neveryone with your message
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.78,0:39:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and scattered the exploding\Npearls to cause mass panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.87,0:40:00.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You then stole the real Black\NStar during the confusion
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.96,0:40:04.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,by pretending to prop her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.25,0:40:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Your pearl is gone, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid! He stole the Black Star!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.22,0:40:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact that you prepared\Nthose fireworks means you knew
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.52,0:40:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she had a large number\Nof replicas made.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.52,0:40:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit joking around, Conan-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.69,0:40:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know which one was\Nreal, and I didn't have any hints!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.32,0:40:37.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't need hints to\Nknow which one was real!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.87,0:40:42.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she took her pearl\Nout with a glove, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.75,0:40:47.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pearls are made of calcium carbonate\Nand are highly reactive to acid.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.67,0:40:53.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oil in the fingers would oxidize\Nthe surface and make it lose its luster.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.26,0:40:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people realized, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.02,0:41:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Realized that she'd never give\Nsuch a delicate jewel to anyone else!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.40,0:41:09.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's not enough to--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.15,0:41:11.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed, that wouldn't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.40,0:41:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But add her dull pearl to the equation\Nand speculation becomes certainty!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.95,0:41:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Just as old pearls in famous\Nmuseums fade in color over time,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.75,0:41:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,a pearl's luster lasts\Na few decades at most.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:31.71,0:41:35.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Black Star was\Npurchased sixty years ago;
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.09,0:41:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it can't possibly look flawless now.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.51,0:41:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it would have been obvious
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.85,0:41:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,once you saw her carefully\Nhandle her faded pearl with gloves!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:49.15,0:41:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Talk about pathetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.02,0:41:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so concerned with\Nyou that I completely forgot!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.49,0:42:00.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But wasn't the Black Star\Nin the museum all shiny?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.58,0:42:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you didn't take it.\NYou knew it was a fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.08,0:42:10.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you challenged\Nher in your second letter
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.67,0:42:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and told her to bring the real one.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:13.92,0:42:17.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You even made\Nsure to write "the real one."
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.26,0:42:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here! If you suspect me that much,\NI'll call a policeman to--
Dialogue: 0,0:42:30.90,0:42:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you disappear\Nlike you did on that roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.36,0:42:39.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't call for the\Npolice that time to spite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.49,0:42:43.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You acted like you were\Nabout to hang-glide out,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.83,0:42:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but you quickly dressed up\Nas an officer during the flash,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.37,0:42:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and hid yourself among them!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.83,0:42:56.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it's senseless\Nto ask for help here...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.09,0:43:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...I set up this 1-on-1\Nmatch out of respect
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.22,0:43:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for the criminal artist who snuck\Non board amidst all the security.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:05.43,0:43:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Most great artists\Nbecome famous after they die.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.77,0:43:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make you a great\Nmaster, Kaitou Kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.19,0:43:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once I place you in\Nthe cemetery known as jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.70,0:43:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I surrender.\NI'll give up on this pearl.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.37,0:43:33.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the lady I'm\Nsorry for ruining the party!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.71,0:43:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you're sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.05,0:43:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! The girl I knocked\Nout to get these clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.47,0:43:46.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll catch cold if we don't hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:46.64,0:43:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a perfectionist, you see!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.02,0:43:54.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another flash grenade!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.98,0:43:56.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.32,0:43:59.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I won't let you escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.95,0:44:06.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.16,0:44:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.55,0:44:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! There's a girl asleep in this boat!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.26,0:44:26.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.81,0:44:31.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing in here?\NAnyway, let's get her out...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.77,0:44:34.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.10,0:44:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't take her out! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.02,0:44:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.61,0:44:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This crimson dress you gave me\Nthe other day suits you wonderfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.33,0:44:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- The Occasional Dry Cleaner, Kaitou Kid"
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.67,0:44:54.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.35,0:45:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They later found the hang glider\NKaitou Kid planned to escape with,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.48,0:45:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he, himself, had completely\Nvanished from the ship.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.41,0:47:05.38,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Grade-schooler Protects Black Star!\NKaitou Kid Thwarted!!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:59.17,0:47:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are! "Grade-schooler\NProtects Black Star!"
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.76,0:47:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a big hero, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:08.42,0:47:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, it was just luck!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.39,0:47:15.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys actually\Nmet the Kid! You're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:15.68,0:47:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.18,0:47:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, what did he look like?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:20.19,0:47:21.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.69,0:47:22.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.48,0:47:23.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Kid's face!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.32,0:47:27.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! He knocked me out too fast...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.44,0:47:29.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw his face, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.78,0:47:32.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of older man was he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.20,0:47:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was surprisingly young.\NIn his twenties, or maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:39.96,0:47:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me your cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:42.50,0:47:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Falling into the ocean while touring\Nthe Selizabeth! Talk about stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.05,0:47:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so annoying.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.84,0:47:53.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's that brat's fault!\NSwimming away was my only option!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.72,0:47:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! That high-schooler...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:57.47,0:47:59.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't he look like Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.85,0:48:01.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.10,0:48:04.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the guy\Nyou saw in Shibuya was...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.74,0:48:11.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whew!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.45,0:48:12.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.33,0:48:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.10,0:48:21.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.95,0:48:23.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.19,0:48:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But where's Mitsuaki-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.14,0:48:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's there. Down below.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.89,0:48:47.90,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Eminent Family's\NStrange Deaths, Part 1
Dialogue: 0,0:48:42.66,0:48:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next Conan:
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.07,0:48:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Case of the Eminent Family's\NStrange Deaths, Part 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.57,0:48:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.74,0:48:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective of the West.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.12,0:48:55.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode airs on October 20th.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.07,0:48:58.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fu-{\i1}kun{\i0}, Ryo-{\i1}kun{\i0}, and Hazuki-{\i1}chan{\i0}, wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.05,0:49:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
